flowchart LR
    subgraph DevZone[Developer Workstation]
        IaC[IaC Modules\nTerraform/CDK/Pulumi]
        Tests[Local Validation\npytest + lint]
        Secrets[Secrets Mgmt\nSOPS/Parameter Store]
    end

    subgraph CICD[CI/CD Control Plane]
        Actions[GitHub Actions\nTerraform pipeline]
        Lint[Format & Schema Checks]
        Scan[Security Scan\ntfsec]
        Plan[Plan & Manual Approval]
    end

    subgraph AWS[AWS Account\n(VPC/Accounts)]
        State[S3 + DynamoDB\nRemote State]
        Network[VPC + Subnets]
        Compute[EKS/ECS/EC2 Targets]
        IAM[IAM Roles & Policies]
        Observability[CloudWatch Metrics/Logs]
    end

    IaC -->|Push IaC| Actions
    Tests -->|Pre-commit| Actions
    Secrets -->|Runtime Secrets| Plan
    Actions --> Lint --> Scan --> Plan
    Plan -->|Apply| Network
    Plan -->|Provision| Compute
    Plan -->|Persist state| State
    Compute --> Observability
    Network --> Observability
    Observability -->|Health signals| Actions
